{
  "page": "Wyl (guard)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Wyl</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">Northmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nUnidentified</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_1\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 1\">Season 1</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Wyl</b> is a young member of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark_guards\" title=\"House Stark guards\">household guard</a> of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wyl_(guard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wyl_(guard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wyl is one of the guards that go south with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a> when he is named <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Jory_Cassel\" title=\"Jory Cassel\">Jory Cassel</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Heward\" title=\"Heward\">Heward</a> and Wyl escort Eddard to a <a href=\"/index.php/Brothel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brothel\">brothel</a> to find one of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastards\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastards\">bastards</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Barra\" title=\"Barra\">Barra</a>. On the return trip to the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">Red Keep</a>, the three guards are slain by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister_guards\" title=\"House Lannister guards\">House Lannister guards</a> under orders from Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> as a lesson to Eddard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wyl_(guard)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Appendix\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 35\">Chapter 35</a>, Eddard IX.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403205233\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.071 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.252 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 465/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10473/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4567/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 482/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 996/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virt